{
  "stem": "13258.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But some people did.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And for-- until 1943, November, 1943, I didn't know what happened to them, because some of the people were our friends who left there.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were taken away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then about 24-- no, 36 hours after we had embarked on the train, the train moved.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the moment the train moved, we knew we were not going to Poland.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We knew we were going to Russia, because one-- of the direction.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But besides, we stopped at a station, which again, in German literature is known, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was a writer, [INAUDIBLE], who wrote a story about that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was not-- knew about that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I knew that story.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we were at [INAUDIBLE], and we went into Russia.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We were on the train about probably 10 days, 12 days.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I don't know exactly.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We went to Kiev.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We were in [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We were in [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We were in [INAUDIBLE], [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We ended in, on the rail, on the railroad line-- on a sideline of the rail line which goes from [INAUDIBLE] to Vladivostok, past the line separating Europe from Si-- from Asia, in Siberia.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the district, or as the [INAUDIBLE], the Russians call it Oblast of Tyuman, which is T-Y-U-M-A-N, County [INAUDIBLE], sector 248 of the [INAUDIBLE] Forest Industry.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was one at the beginning, one-- what do you call-- block, round, buildings-- a log cabin.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One huge log cabin divided in several--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--parts on the one side of the railroad tracks, a more modern barracks building on the other side of the railroad tracks, and a couple single houses about two or three miles away-- all together about 1,000 people in that settlement.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "First days of July-- 10th, 15th, about between 10th and 15th of July, 1940.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The same evening, we were assigned places.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
